com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers.readonly

Class ReadOnlyGraph<T extends Graph>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers.readonly.ReadOnlyGraph<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph, WrapperGraph<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadOnlyIndexableGraph

    public class ReadOnlyGraph<T extends Graph>
extends Object
implements Graph, WrapperGraph<T>
    A ReadOnlyGraph wraps a Graph and overrides the underlying graph's mutating methods. In this way, a ReadOnlyGraph can only be read from, not written to.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
